WEBVTT

1
00:10:35.830 --> 00:10:38.400 
这些关注压得我喘不过气
I'm overwhelmed by all this attention.

2
00:10:41.340 --> 00:10:42.870 
明早我就要上电视了
I'm gonna be on TV in the morning.

3
00:10:43.040 --> 00:10:44.920 
他们会问我什么呢 我该怎么回答
What ave they gonna ask me? What am I gonna say?

4
00:10:45.070 --> 00:10:47.180 
萨利 需要我去陪你吗
Sully, do you want me to come be with you?

5
00:10:47.540 --> 00:10:49.250 
不用了 洛丽
No, Lorrie.

6
00:10:49.840 --> 00:10:51.880 
谢谢 但是女儿们需要你
Thanks, but the girls need you.

7
00:10:52.850 --> 00:10:54.350 
告诉她们 我爱她们
Tell them I love them.

8
00:10:55.350 --> 00:10:57.690 
我爱你 睡个好觉
I love you. Get some sleep.

9
00:10:58.250 --> 00:10:59.430 
是呀
Yeah.

10
00:10:59.590 --> 00:11:02.030 
或许一觉醒来 就是1月14日了
Hey, maybe when I wake up, it'll be January 14th.

11
00:11:02.190 --> 00:11:03.360 
那样岂不是很棒
Wouldn't that be good?

